{% comment %}
  Free Shipping Threshold Snippet

  Outputs the free shipping threshold as a formatted dollar amount.
  Pulls from Theme Settings cart_goal_1_threshold.

  Usage:
    {% render 'free-shipping-threshold' %}
    Output: $60

  The threshold is set in Theme Settings > Cart Goals > Goal 1 Threshold
{% endcomment %}

{%- liquid
  assign threshold_dollars = settings.cart_goal_1_threshold | default: 60 | round
-%}
${{ threshold_dollars -}}
